divs: Sighting Detailsmy husband and i were walking our dogs,when we noticed this low flying object,round star like.it went from nw to se and it made no noise. we watched it until it just faded out. we know it was some type of unusual object.we both felt a little shocked and my dog would not move for a minute or two,she refused to move.
